{"tid":1599801,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"願榮光 - 何君堯版","createTime":"2019-09-28T08:00:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T17:35:49.000Z","uid":42246,"like":7,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"cba4ef89938de33deb4c15b17a9cae3c9cd054bd","tid":1599801,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T08:00:06.000Z","msg":"《願榮光歸香港》連日在香港各區響起，成為反送中運動抗爭主題由，惟有人早前利用《榮光》原曲改上「止暴制亂」、反暴力的新詞，親中陣營仿效早前《榮光》自製管弦樂版 MV ，今日在 Youtube 推出「《願平安歸香港》管弦樂團及合唱團版 MV」，建制派立法會議員何君堯更在 MV 中領唱，「齊來同對抗   今日混亂香港 」。<br />\n<br />\n製作者自稱是一群「愛香港文化藝術工作者」，他們又稱，「音符無分界限，相信填上不同的歌詞， 也可以凝聚和傳頌我們 750-201 萬（編按：？）香港人的想法。 支持香港警察，嚴正執法。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%9D%87%E7%89%87-%E9%A1%98%E6%A6%AE%E5%85%89-%E8%A2%AB%E6%94%B9%E6%AD%A2%E6%9A%B4%E5%88%B6%E4%BA%82%E7%89%88-%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF-mv-%E9%A0%98%E5%94%B1-%E5%B0%8D%E6%9A%B4%E5%BE%92%E9%BD%8A%E4%BE%86%E7%94%A8%E6%AD%A3%E6%B0%A3/?fbclid=IwAR08h1I48ejMXAcyVuPnqZjAesM3EJ_up61JlAjTcxElyCjBYr2AFWBpTbU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%259D%2587%25E7%2589%2587-%25E9%25A1%2598%25E6%25A6%25AE%25E5%2585%2589-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%2594%25B9%25E6%25AD%25A2%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%2588%25B6%25E4%25BA%2582%25E7%2589%2588-%25E4%25BD%2595%25E5%2590%259B%25E5%25A0%25AF-mv-%25E9%25A0%2598%25E5%2594%25B1-%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%25BE%2592%25E9%25BD%258A%25E4%25BE%2586%25E7%2594%25A8%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E6%25B0%25A3%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR08h1I48ejMXAcyVuPnqZjAesM3EJ_up61JlAjTcxElyCjBYr2AFWBpTbU&d=%2F9qUFN9YWCJnPZyZgWzOjwWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=c63000fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%259D%2587%25E7%2589%2587-%25E9%25A1%2598%25E6%25A6%25AE%25E5%2585%2589-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%2594%25B9%25E6%25AD%25A2%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%2588%25B6%25E4%25BA%2582%25E7%2589%2588-%25E4%25BD%2595%25E5%2590%259B%25E5%25A0%25AF-mv-%25E9%25A0%2598%25E5%2594%25B1-%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%25BE%2592